Interface Status

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Status>, EntitySupport, Serializable, TwitterResponse

    public interface Status
extends Comparable<Status>, TwitterResponse, EntitySupport, Serializable
    A data interface representing one single status of a user.
    Author:
    Yusuke Yamamoto - yusuke at mac.com
